<br>
Lightning Reflexes; This ability increases your chance of completely avoiding incoming melee damage<br>
Innate Defense; This ability expans on the Combat Stability skill reducing the amount of damage done to the character even further.<br>
<br>
They are an update for CS, CA but so far I havent found any information how much % of mitigation and avoidance they bring with each lvl trained. (CA, CS was, 2,5%;5%,10%)<br>
Dont wanna spend 2,4,6,8,10 AA points if they only give a like 1% better mitigation or avoidance. So does anyone have found some more information or made a parse on it?<br>
<br>
Altough I am a Paladin I hope I get an answer ... the Pala board couldnt. many thx in advance<br>
